{"type": "article", "id": 10583, "title": "Spun 铜碗与种植器皿", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-10T07:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235757Mt8EGrUYyN6F0x93.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tAndrew Deming 和 Rachel Gant 两位设计师在美国旧金山圣奥古斯丁创立了设计工作室 Yield，日前他们推出了最新款的碗 Spun Bowl 与种植器皿 Spun Planter 。Spun Bowl 分为金色铜制款鱼银色的钢制款，既可以用于厨房烹饪，亦可以用作低矮的植物种植器皿。而 Planter 则是专门用来种植较高的植物，底部还专门设计了一块穿孔板，避免植物被过多的水浸泡。两款新品造型简洁，仅用最原始的铜与钢的材质表达含蓄的优雅，定价 80－110 美元（约合人民币 496－683 元），<a href=\"http://www.yielddesign.co/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235754yxsSZ5hQ8I34RJmY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052357557h1gVuefjbBRsWdm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235755YHctbr1C6zZFUaKA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235756ZLoPD2B8sRNgeXWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235756U423jfOMbvQgAVpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}